[size=150][b]Features[/b][/size]
[list][*] Ability to install buttons by dropping Custom Button URIs or XML files into ANY toolbar. XML files can be installed in bulk. [b]Beware!!![/b] If 10 XML files are dropped into ANY toolbar, all 10 buttons will be installed and all 10 alert boxes will be displayed after each installation.
[*] Ability to group menu items into [i]"menugroup"[/i] elements. See images.
[*] Ability to show/hide individual menu items.
[*] Ability to import individual buttons in bulk from backed-up overlay files (ProfileFolder/custombuttons/buttonsoverlay.xul).[/list]

